00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:29.610
Spirit Dew?

00:37:30.760 --> 00:37:31.820
Pinag-isipan ka!

00:38:06.800 --> 00:38:07.490
Kanina...

00:38:09.030 --> 00:38:10.260
